OL,7,GThe BBC's Annual Plan for the 12
OL,8,Gmonths starting 1st April provides a
OL,9,Gmore detailed look at what the BBC
OL,10,Ghas planned for its services.
OL,12,FOfcom will judge the BBC based on the
OL,13,Fcommitments that appear in the
OL,14,Fdocument, in line with the recently
OL,15,Frevised operating licence.
OL,17,FBut following two years of a frozen
OL,18,Flicence fee, the BBC's deficit for
OL,19,Fthe year now stands at #352m with the
OL,20,Fbroadcaster seeking to make #400m of
OL,21,Fsavings.
OL,3,CBBC Annual Plan: more cuts, reliance
OL,4,Con commercial growth and review of
OL,5,Cradio portfolio
