OL,7,FIt's pinning its hopes on a growth
OL,8,Fplan for BBC Studios, which aims to
OL,9,Fplug some of the shortfall and
OL,10,Fgenerate further income for the BBC.
OL,11,FIn the UK, the annual plan confirms
OL,12,Fthe BBC will aim to increase the
OL,13,Freach and share of its UKTV broadcast
OL,14,Fbusiness.
OL,16,FAs a result of the cuts, there will
OL,17,Fbe fewer new shows alongside the
OL,18,Fpreviously announced cuts to local
OL,19,Fradio and merger of its news
OL,20,Fchannels.
