OL,7,FRegarding news, the BBC has been hit
OL,8,Fby a triple whammy of
OL,10,FBBC Global News Limited, which looks
OL,11,Fafter the sales of advertising on BBC
OL,12,FWorld News, has posted losses for the
OL,13,Fpast three years. Back in 2017,
OL,14,Fformer BBC Director-General Tony Hall
OL,15,Fpleaded for extra money from the
OL,16,FGovernment for BBC World News.
