OL,7,FThe hope is by merging the two
OL,8,Fchannels, a more premium product can
OL,9,Fbe created on limited resources,
OL,10,Falthough there are ongoing concerns
OL,11,Fabout UK audiences being
OL,12,Fdisadvantaged.
OL,14,FIn turn, the new BBC News service
OL,15,Fwould be better able to cover its
OL,16,Fcosts through advertising and
OL,17,Fsponsorship outside of the UK.
