OL,7,FThe BBC doubled down on plans to cut
OL,8,FBBC Local Radio, despite strong
OL,9,Fobjections and ongoing industrial
OL,10,Faction. The NUJ continues a work to
OL,11,Frule in BBC Local, which resulted in
OL,12,Fno separate regional TV news service
OL,13,Ffor the North East and Cumbria this
OL,14,Fmorning.
