OL,7,FNevertheless, the BBC confirmed work
OL,8,Fwould continue to ensure that all
OL,9,Fregional news studios are refreshed
OL,10,Fand can output in HD. Despite the
OL,11,Farrival of BBC One HD, some regions
OL,12,Fstill broadcast in SD ` something
OL,13,Fthat is now confirmed to change in
OL,14,Fthe coming operational year.
