OL,7,FOn radio, the BBC is to review how it
OL,8,Fuses DAB digital radio. In a vague
OL,9,Fstatement, the broadcaster said it
OL,10,Fwill also review its portfolio of
OL,11,Fsmaller services. Previously it had
OL,12,Fannounced an online-only move for
OL,13,FRadio 4 Extra, but the annual plan
OL,14,Ffailed to provide any further
OL,15,Fspecifics.
OL,17,FMeanwhile the BBC will finalise plans
OL,18,Fto close BBC Radio 5 Live on Medium
OL,19,FWave and stop scheduling separate
OL,20,Fprogrammes on R4 LW ahead of its
OL,21,Fclosure.
