OL,7,FOn TV, the BBC promises to screen
OL,8,F7,775 hours of first-run programmes
OL,9,Fin 2023 ` 24 across BBC One (4,500
OL,10,Fhours), BBC Two (2,600 hours), BBC
OL,11,FThree (200 hours), BBC Four (150
OL,12,Fhours), CBBC (250) and CBeebies
OL,13,F(100).
OL,15,FMany more hours of content will be on
OL,16,Fthe iPlayer only.
