OL,7,FFor example, 500 hours of history
OL,8,Fprogrammes will be made available to
OL,9,Fviewers in 2023 ` 24. 400 hours will
OL,10,Fappear on regular TV channels, while
OL,11,F100 hours will be iPlayer only. But
OL,12,Fonly 40 hours will be first-run.
OL,14,FIn science/natural history, 800 of
OL,15,Fthe 1,000 hours of content to be made
OL,16,Favailable will be broadcast on
OL,17,Fregular channels, with 200 hours
OL,18,Fonline only.
