OL,7,F140 of the overall entertainment/
OL,8,Ffactual hours will be acquisitions of
OL,9,Fwhich only a third will be shown on
OL,10,FTV channels; the remainder will be
OL,11,Fonline only.
OL,13,FAt the same time, more of the BBC's
OL,14,FTV and radio programmes will be made
