OL,8,Foperating licence saw the BBC appeal
OL,9,Ffor a greater relaxation of quotas.
OL,10,FIn the end, Ofcom decided to retain
OL,11,Fsome quotas and turn back on plans to
OL,12,Fremove all commitments from BBC News.
